snippet.title: Trials of Mana - Nintendo Direct 9.4.2019 - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
When these six destinies intertwine, the world will be born anew. Trials of Mana arrives on Nintendo Switch on April 24, 2020. Available now: https://nintendo.com/games/detail/trials-of-mana-switch/
